# QuickNote CLI

A tiny command-line tool to create, list and remove short notes stored locally in a JSON file.

## Features
- Add a quick note

## Requirements
- Python 3.8+

## Installation (local)
```bash
git clone https://github.com/<your-username>/quicknote-cli.git
cd quicknote-cli
python -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate    # on Windows: venv\Scripts\activate
pip install -r requirements.txt
# add a note
python quicknote.py add "Buy milk"

# list notes
python quicknote.py list

# delete a note
python quicknote.py delete 2

---

### `.gitignore`

- List all notes
- Delete a note by ID
